# Product ranking (in-place)

- **DDL**: `product_rank_scores`, `ez_product_penalties` in [`ez_bootstrap_custom_tables.sql`](wp-content/mu-plugins/ez_core/database/sql/ez_bootstrap_custom_tables.sql).
- **Module**: `EscapeZoom\Core\Modules\ProductRanking` ‚Äî Capsule/Eloquent only in Services/Repositories (no `$wpdb` / `mysqli`).
- **Legacy event tables** (no WP prefix): `hottest_products`, `held_orders_list`, `product_views`.
- **Booking DB**: `CapsuleBoot::CONNECTION_ESCAPEZO` + table `zb_booking_history` for topsale eligibility.
- **Theme**: thin hooks + `do_action('ez_ranking_recalculate')`; wizard in `inc/core/product-ranking/`.
- **Do not** write carousel sort to external `products_order` or snapshot `rank_*` columns (join `product_rank_scores` instead).
